Class TestManager

java.lang.Object
  commodities.tests.TestManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
ContractSelectionListener, EventListener, PriceListener
public class TestManager
extends Object
implements PriceListener, ContractSelectionListener

The TestManager class controls what tests are available to the system and how they are accessed.
